    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253300/extras/6422c36a1362ccc03af3f75acfc32a72.poster.avif?t=1732659042\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253300/extras/6422c36a1362ccc03af3f75acfc32a72.webm?t=1732659042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short game of Hangman with a dark twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One level. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(Or is it?) </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >F̴̧̟̥̞̻̖͙͚͓̈́Į̶̨̧̺̮͉̏̏̒̏̑̎̍̌̏̇̚N̴̡̺͇̗͈͙̣̲̅̀͂̏̑̀̂̽̉́͋͝D̸̼͔͉͇̭͇̥͗͑̀̌̕͜ ̴͎̥̞̪̇͌͑̕M̴̢̛͍̖̲͙͇̤̫̖͗̐̂̄̎̐́͐̾͊̽͊̀̚Ȇ̷͍̲̱̥̀̐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally posted on Itch and made for the GAM135 course at USV in under three weeks. <strong>Now on Steam with a new, major update - will you find it? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potential to be updated with even more content in the future but for now, enjoy this short experience of the game we all know. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>(Includes Random Word Mode) </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be sure to check out our links, discord, and upcoming games! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >xxx </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pixel Poxet <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253300/extras/8db96ac3fa6cbe1cda2ae12c8b287592.avif?t=1732659042\" width=726 height=350 /></span></p>",
